{"word":"σωρεύω","slug":"σωρεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σωρεύω</b></el> <el>(σωρεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-εύσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σωρός'><el>σωρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to heap</i> one thing <i>on</i> another, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>coacervare</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to heap with</i> something, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}